Comair operations suspended indefinitely. This follows Saturday's temporary suspension of Comair's Kulula and British Airways flights. #eNCA's Heidi Giokos has the latest on this story. #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - The Civil Aviation Authority says Comair flights have been suspended indefinitely. The authority says their findings mean there is an immediate risk to safety and security. Passengers at OR Tambo International have been left frustrated by the Civil Aviation Authority's grounding of flights.